WEBVTT

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:22.000
Host: The Republic of Alernia has issued a civil warning to all citizens. A classified specimen has escaped from the national laboratory. An emergency has been declared in the nation.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:31.000
Host: If you see an exigent homunculus-esque creature outside your home, lock all doors, turn off all lights and anything powered by electricity.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:41.500
Host: Go into a basement, closet, or barricaded room. Do not leave until the creature has seized all noise. After the end of all noises, call authorities immediately.

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:46.800
Host: Anyone interacting with this creature shall be considered a fugitive if they live long enough.